                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-322-off1656 t18310908-322-cd1657"></join>, 1 boy's dress, value 5s.; 1 shirt, value 2s.; 1 pair of boots, value 2s.; 1 frill and collar,<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183109080138"></xptr>value 1s., and 1 pinafore, value 1s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18310908-322-victim2324" type="victimName">
